### Listar pets disponíveis (rota pública)
GET http://localhost:3000/pets/available


### Login como admin (necessário para as rotas protegidas abaixo)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ifrs.edu.br",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Substitua {{token_admin}} com o token gerado acima
# Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}


### Listar todos os pets (somente admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}


### Buscar pet por ID (somente admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}


### Cadastrar novo pet (somente admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Frajola",
  "age": 3,
  "species": "cat",
  "size": "small",           // small | medium | large
  "description": "Gato preto e branco, muito brincalhão"
}

### Atualizar pet (somente admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Frajola Atualizado",
  "age": 4,
  "species": "cat",
  "size": "small",           // small | medium | large
  "description": "Atualizado pelo admin"
}

### Remover pet (somente admin - precisa estar 'available')
DELETE http://localhost:3000/pets/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token_admin}}
